textfsm_template:
Value DOMAIN_NAME (\S+)
Value REGISTRY_DOMAIN_ID (\S+)
Value REGISTRAR_WHOIS_SERVER (\S+)
Value REGISTRAR_URL (\S+)
Value UPDATED_DATE (\S+)
Value CREATION_DATE (\S+)
Value REGISTRY_EXPIRY_DATE (\S+)
Value REGISTRAR (\S+(?:\s+\S+)*)
Value REGISTRAR_IANA_ID (\d+)
Value REGISTRAR_ABUSE_CONTACT_EMAIL (\S+)
Value REGISTRAR_ABUSE_CONTACT_PHONE (\S+)
Value DOMAIN_STATUS (\S+\s+\S+)
Value NAME_SERVER (\S+)
Value DNSSEC (\S+)

Start
  ^\s*Domain Name:\s*${DOMAIN_NAME}$$
  ^\s*Registry Domain ID:\s*${REGISTRY_DOMAIN_ID}$$
  ^\s*Registrar WHOIS Server:\s*${REGISTRAR_WHOIS_SERVER}$$
  ^\s*Registrar URL:\s*${REGISTRAR_URL}$$
  ^\s*Updated Date:\s*${UPDATED_DATE}$$
  ^\s*Creation Date:\s*${CREATION_DATE}$$
  ^\s*Registry Expiry Date:\s*${REGISTRY_EXPIRY_DATE}$$
  ^\s*Registrar:\s*${REGISTRAR}$$
  ^\s*Registrar IANA ID:\s*${REGISTRAR_IANA_ID}$$
  ^\s*Registrar Abuse Contact Email:\s*${REGISTRAR_ABUSE_CONTACT_EMAIL}$$
  ^\s*Registrar Abuse Contact Phone:\s*${REGISTRAR_ABUSE_CONTACT_PHONE}$$
  ^\s*Domain Status:\s*${DOMAIN_STATUS}$$
  ^\s*Name Server:\s*${NAME_SERVER}$$
  ^\s*DNSSEC:\s*${DNSSEC}$$ -> Record
